title: Bushwick Brooklyn gallery tour
desc: Our Bushwick Brooklyn tour will happen in New York?s newest important art neighborhood, with over 50 galleries showing work by mostly emerging artists.? Be sure to arrive early or on time, so that the tour doesn?t leave without you.? All sales are final, and tickets are valid only for the date for which it was purchased.? Tours take place no matter the temperature or weather, as the art is all indoors.
